<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ن ظ ف:</span> <span class="c2">(النَّظَافَةُ)</span> النَّقَاوَةُ وَقَدْ <span class="c2">(نَظُفَ)</span> الشَّيْءُ مِنْ بَابِ ظَرُفَ فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(نَظِيفٌ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(نَظَّفَهُ)</span> غَيْرُهُ <span class="c2">(تَنْظِيفًا)</span> أَيْ نَقَّاهُ. وَ <span class="c2">(التَّنَظُّفُ)</span> تَكَلُّفُ النَّظَافَةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>